Title: Gender Bender
Plot: A series of sexually-oriented murders, which are identical except that the killer appears to be both male and female, draws Scully and Mulder to an Amish-type community of people called the Kindred.
GuestStars: Brent Hinkley, David Thomson, Kate Twa, Peter Stebbings, Mitchell Kosterman, Michele Goodger, Aundrea MacDonald, John R. Taylor, Grai Carrington, Tony Morelli, Lesley Ewen, Nicholas Lea, Paul Batten, Doug Abraham
